### Youyu - Payment
### Prerequisite: backend started with -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=seed
### Run an order checkout first, then replace @orderId and @paymentNo as needed.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@buyerToken = mock-1001-USER
@otherUserToken = mock-1004-USER
@orderId = 1
@paymentNo = PAY2026052700000001

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Gateway
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Get payment gateway info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/gateway
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Get payment gateway info without auth - expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/gateway

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Initiation
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Initiate payment for an order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/orders/{{orderId}}/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Initiate payment as non-buyer - expect 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/orders/{{orderId}}/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### Duplicate payment for an order with active payment - expect BUSINESS_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/orders/{{orderId}}/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Mock success
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Complete mock payment success
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/{{paymentNo}}/mock-success
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Complete mock payment success as non-buyer - expect 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/{{paymentNo}}/mock-success
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### Duplicate mock success - expect BUSINESS_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/{{paymentNo}}/mock-success
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
